**Open Graph** is a protocol which enables rich previews on social media. It is heavily used on the web and different messenger apps. See [[https://ogp.me]]

MycorrhizaWiki supports it and outputs the needed meta tags to enable previews.

* **The name** is hypha's name.
* **The image** is the first image hypha embeds. If the hypha //is// an image, that image is shown. If there is no image, favicon is shown instead.
* **The description** is hypha's first paragraph.
